org.sql: SELECT attachments.* FROM attachments LEFT JOIN documents ON attachments.container_type = 'Document' AND documents.id = attachments.container_id LEFT JOIN projects ON documents.project_id = projects.id WHERE attachments.created_on BETWEEN '2022-02-04' AND '2022-02-14' AND attachments.author_id = 2 AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'documents') IS NOT NULL
